- cs.CY (Computers and Society): The paper discusses the stability of online user communities and the role of moderators in enforcing good behavior, which is a topic related to the intersection of computers and society. 
- cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences): The paper analyzes the behavior of users and moderators in online communities, which is a topic related to social and behavioral sciences. 
- cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction): The paper discusses the role of moderators in motivating good behavior among users, which is a topic related to human-computer interaction.
